text.en_US: Seems you cannot just simply teleport to the other side.
If you hold on to the block before it gets teleported...
You will warp with the block and not be on the moving platform!
Try standing on the middle of this floor pattern first.
This will cause Lea to walk up to the block a bit before grabbing it from this position.
Stand there and warp the block into the right teleporter.
Right before the block gets warped you want to grab it without moving.
The result you should get is Lea snapping to the block's new position.
However, the side and direction she is facing is wrong.
With this state you can push the block up and clip through the fence!
The window of the grab timing increases the farther away you are from the block when you try holding on to it.
If this glitchy state seems too tight to do in some situations, always remember to readjust where you are standing!
